{"tid":2074243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠：基本法誕生即與《聯合聲明》切割了","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T04:01:19.000Z","uid":279819,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dae76bdb8cd4717a2333cfb5aec0946284a87e","tid":2074243,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:16:45.000Z","msg":"近年外國勢力插手香港事務時，只提《中英聯合聲明》（《聯合聲明》）而不提基本法，基本法委員會副主任、原基本法起草委員會委員譚惠珠表示，<ins>《聯合聲明》屬於中英雙方各自表述</ins>，但基本法體現的全部是中國的具體聲明，「基本法誕生之時就與《聯合聲明》切割了」。<br />\n<br />\n對於反對派拒絕承認中央對香港擁有全面管治權，聲稱這是《聯合聲明》之外的「僭建」。譚惠珠直言：「這完全是錯的，因為中國無需和英國說明中央與地方關係如何處理，《聯合聲明》全部講『兩制』，很少講『一國』，『一國兩制』的實體在基本法中，不在《聯合聲明》中。」<br />\n...................<br />\n<a href=\"https://old.dotdotnews.com/2020/03/26/breakingnews/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%9530%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%EF%BD%9C%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%B3%E8%88%87%E3%80%8A%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fold.dotdotnews.com%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fbreakingnews%2F%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%259530%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25EF%25BD%259C%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%2588%2587%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0Fy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=227203c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://old.dotdotnews.com/2020/03/26/breakingnews/%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%9530%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%EF%BD%9C%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F%E5%8D%B3%E8%88%87%E3%80%8A%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E</a>"},{"pid":"6b5fce594c9ad5f34dabcb9cce9e09ab7129439b","tid":2074243,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"九千幾種講法，夾好口供先啦"},{"pid":"a849b019079567a70fbe88bf17ff16367366b09e","tid":2074243,"uid":